name: 揮刺
note:
<Custom Requirement>
   if (a.isStateAffected(51)) {
     value = true;
   } else {
     value = false;
   }
</Custom Requirement>

<damage formula>
value = 25 * a.atk / 100;
if (b.isStateAffected(5)){
value *= 1.1
}
if (b.isStateAffected(8)){
value *= 1.1
}
if (b.isStateAffected(11)){
value *= 1.1
}
if (b.isStateAffected(19)){
value *= 1.1
}
value -= b.def / 100
if (b.isStateAffected(23)){
value *= 1.1
}
if (b.isStateAffected(52) || b.isStateAffected(53)){
value *= 0
}
</damage formula>
